OL,6,FThe Only Way is Essex star Lauren
OL,7,FGoodger, as well as Biggs Chris and
OL,8,FRebecca Gormley, who both appeared on
OL,9,Fseries six of Love Island, are among
OL,10,Fthose accused of issuing unauthorised
OL,11,Fcommunications of financial promotions.
