OL,3,CInfluencers charged over promoting
OL,4,Cunauthorised financial investments
OL,6,FCFDs are a high risk-investment
OL,7,Fproduct which is used to bet on the
OL,8,Fprice of an asset - in this case the
OL,9,Fprice of foreign currencies.
OL,11,FEighty percent of customers who invest
OL,12,Fin them lose their money.
OL,14,FThe influencers, who are due to appear
OL,15,Fat Westminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,F13 June 2024, face up to two years in
OL,17,Fprison if convicted.
